doc.after: In 1981 Gulfstream introduced the Gulfstream GIIB The GIIB had a modified GII fuselage and the GIII wings complete with winglets The variant offered weight and performance characteristics similar to the GIII but with the shorter GII fuselage Gulfstream completed and delivered approximately 40 GIIBs 2
